Class AddSourceView

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class AddSourceView
extends javafx.scene.layout.HBox
    A box of buttons that let the user add different kinds of Sources. Depending on which button is pressed, a different dialog is presented for the user to construct that source. As an example, the image file source results in a file picker that the user can use to browse for an image.
